{"arkId":"cl010097266","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010097266","modified ":"2025-11-03","title":"Montre \u00e0 double bo\u00eetier","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"Titre","value":"Montre \u00e0 double bo\u00eetier"}],"displayDateCreated":"Epoque \/ p\u00e9riode : Louis XIV (1643-1715) (Occident-\u003E\u00e9poque moderne = Ancien R\u00e9gime-\u003Edynastie des Bourbons)\r\n\r\nDate de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : 1685 - 1700","currentLocation":"Richelieu, [OArt] Salle 531 - Paul Garnier, Vitrine 1","room":"Salle 531, Aile Aile Richelieu, Niveau 1","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":1685,"endYear":1700,"imprecision":"","text":"Fin du XVIIe si\u00e8cle","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[{"label":"Corderoy, Philippe","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","creatorRole":"Horloger","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":""}],"objectNumber":[{"value":"OA 685","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"horlogerie ; montre","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"Montre \u00e0 double bo\u00eetier, bo\u00eetier grav\u00e9 de rinceaux \u00e0 feuilles d\u0027acanthes peupl\u00e9s d\u0027oiseaux, lapins et d\u0027un \u00e9cureuil ; sur le pourtour une frise grav\u00e9e ajour\u00e9e de rinceaux au milieu desquels serpentent deux dragons entrecoup\u00e9s de cinq colonnes doriques. Lunette du verre grav\u00e9e de feuilles stylis\u00e9es. Cloche fix\u00e9e dans le fond, trois trous de remontages marqu\u00e9s \u0022W, C, L.\u0022, b\u00e9li\u00e8re en forme de boule. Bo\u00eetier de protection en cuir clout\u00e9. Cadran \u00e0 chiffres romains et losanges (demi-heures), cadran du r\u00e9veil \u00e0 chiffres arabes grav\u00e9 d\u0027un motif de feuillage, index en laiton. Mouvement \u00e0 sonnerie et \u00e0 r\u00e9veil muni d\u0027un \u00e9chappement \u00e0 roue de rencontre, une fus\u00e9e avec cha\u00eene, un balancier \u00e0 ressort-spiral-r\u00e9glant, coq circulaire \u00e0 un pied grav\u00e9 et ajour\u00e9 de rinceaux. Roue de compte de la sonnerie num\u00e9rot\u00e9e 1 \u00e0 12, un des trois barillets ajour\u00e9 et grav\u00e9, un autre grav\u00e9.","inscriptions":"Signature : \r ; mouvement sign\u00e9 : Philip Corderoy London","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","value":"8,8","displayDimension":"8,8 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Largeur","value":"7","displayDimension":"7 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":2,"note":""},{"type":"Profondeur","value":"4","displayDimension":"4 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":3,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"Mat\u00e9riau : argent\r\nMat\u00e9riau : laiton\r\nMat\u00e9riau : peau = cuir\r\nTechnique : techniques m\u00e9tal (orf\u00e8vrerie)\r\nTechnique : \u00e9maill\u00e9 = \u00e9maillage = \u00e9mail = \u00e9maux (techniques m\u00e9tal)","placeOfCreation":"Londres (Grande-Bretagne = Grande Bretagne-\u003EAngleterre)","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"collection Alexandre-Charles Sauvageot (1781-1860) ; acquise en 1835, cf. le Livre d\u0027achat n\u00b0 1504 : \u0022Grosse montre en argent cisel\u00e9 \u00e0 r\u00e9veil avec double bo\u00eete, datant de Louis XIV. 120 francs. Rest[auration] de la bo\u00eete, 12 francs, du mouvement, 30 francs \/ 162 francs\u0022 ; donation accept\u00e9e en 1856, acte notari\u00e9 le 6 mars 1857, n\u00b0 1365 : \u0022Gros r\u00e9veil, dans sa bo\u00eete en argent grav\u00e9 et cisel\u00e9 \u00e0 jour sur les c\u00f4t\u00e9s, cadran en argent double bo\u00eete en cuivre noir, estim\u00e9 deux-cents francs\u0022.","jabachInventory":"","napoleonInventory":"","previousOwner":[{"value":"M. Sauvageot, Alexandre-Charles","note":"","role":", Collectionneur ; Donateur"}],"acquisitionDetails":[{"mode":"donation","doubt":"","dates":[{"type":"date de donation","value":"1856","startYear":1856,"endYear":1856}]}],"ownedBy":"Etat","heldBy":"Mus\u00e9e du Louvre, D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","longTermLoanTo":"","index":{"Mode d\u0027acquisition":[{"value":"donation"}],"period":[{"value":"Louis XIV (1643-1715)"}],"place":[{"value":"Londres"}],"objectType":[{"value":"horlogerie"},{"value":"montre"}]},"bibliography":[{"bibliographyRef":"Cardinal, Catherine, Les montres et horloges de table du mus\u00e9e du Louvre, Tome 2, Paris, RMN, 2000","bibliographyDate":"2000","bibliographyDetail":"p. 156-157, n\u00b0 147","comparison":false},{"bibliographyRef":"Darcel, Alfred, Notice des \u00e9maux et de l\u2019orf\u00e8vrerie: S\u00e9rie D [3e \u00e9d. avec suppl. par E. Molinier], Paris, Imprimeries R\u00e9unies, 1883","bibliographyDate":"1883","bibliographyDetail":"p. 528, D 867","comparison":false},{"bibliographyRef":"Sauzay, Alexandre, Mus\u00e9e Imp\u00e9rial du Louvre. Catalogue du Mus\u00e9e Sauvageot, Paris, Impr. Charles de Mourgues, fr\u00e8res, 1861","bibliographyDate":"1861","bibliographyDetail":"p. 98, n\u00b0 438","comparison":false}],"exhibition":[],"relatedWork":[],"image":[{"urlImage":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/media\/cache\/large\/0000000021\/0000097266\/0000745115_OG.JPG","urlThumbnail":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/media\/cache\/small\/0000000021\/0000097266\/0000745115_OG.JPG","copyright":"\u00a9 2017 Mus\u00e9e du Louvre \/ D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","type":"","position":0},{"urlImage":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/media\/cache\/large\/0000000021\/0000097266\/0000745116_OG.JPG","urlThumbnail":"https:\/\/collections